list.comment: Former work husband. Current friend for life. I will always be one of his biggest fans. #ScandalFam @networkbway @americansonplay #networkbway

Happy birthday to my work husband @stevepasquale 😍 I cannot imagine facing this challenge 8x’s a week with any other human. Steve, thank you for saying “yes”. Thank you for revealing your soul up there. Thank you for making me a better actor. And thank you for all the love you bring to this pretend broken marriage of ours. XOXOXOXOXOXOXO #americansonplay #WeCleanedUpGoodForOpeningNight
It's such an honor and a joy to get to work on this important project with you @iamKennyLeon. I adore you!!!!!!! #AmericanSonPlay

Last night we had the privilege of seeing @mockingbirdbway. I was so DEEPLY moved by this gorgeous new exploration of one of our most important and beloved narratives. The writing. The acting. The set design. I was transported. And inspired. And deeply grateful to all the artists and artisans who are telling this story. #ShubertAlleyNeighbors #MockingbirdBway

Today we did a little @AmericanSonPlay press at @sardisnyc. My caricature was right behind me. It was drawn ten years ago during my first time on Broadway performing “Race” #AmericanSonPlay

‪Last night’s @oppagenda talkback after @AmericanSonPlay was extraordinary. thank you to @theCCR, @VinceWarren, @aliciagarza, our entire cast, @iamKENNYLEON and ALL the audience members who stayed to talk about feelings/issues raised by the play & how to be part of the solution!‬ It was tremendously inspiring. I’m gonna retweet some of my favorite moments from the evening now... XO #americansonplay #FutureOverFear #BlackLivesMatter #OppAgenda

HAPPY BIRTHDAY @jeremymjordan 😍
Onstage he is my nemesis but in life he is one of my heroes!
Jeremy, you will NEVER understand how much I have learned from you in the process of bringing @americansonplay to life. Your courage, commitment, talent and work ethic are mind blowing. I pray that I face life’s challenges with the grace, strength and integrity that you have brought to this company. That moment when we finally get to smile at each other during curtain call, it’s always a moment I cherish. It will be especially great tonight. Happy birthday!!!!! 🙏🏾 #AmericanSonPlay
